        {
          "arguments": {
            "content": "{\n  \"files\": [\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/core/css/resolver/style_resolver.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/core/layout/layout_object.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/core/paint/paint_layer.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/platform/graphics/paint/display_item_list.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/platform/graphics/paint/paint_controller.h\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"symbols\": [\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/core/css/resolver/style_resolver.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"StyleResolver\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/core/layout/layout_object.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"LayoutObject\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/core/paint/paint_layer.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"PaintLayer\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/platform/graphics/paint/display_item_list.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"DisplayItemList\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"third_party/blink/renderer/platform/graphics/paint/paint_controller.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"PaintController\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"text\": \"The Blink rendering pipeline processes CSS style changes through multiple stages:\\n\\n1. **Style Resolution** (StyleResolver): Located in third_party/blink/renderer/core/css/resolver/style_resolver.h, the StyleResolver class (line 63) computes ComputedStyle for DOM elements. It matches CSS rules against elements and produces the resolved computed styles that drive the layout and paint phases.\\n\\n2. **Layout Tree** (LayoutObject): The base class LayoutObject is defined in third_party/blink/renderer/core/layout/layout_object.h (line 270). Each DOM element with content has a corresponding LayoutObject in the layout tree, responsible for computing layout dimensions and positions.\\n\\n3. **Paint Layers** (PaintLayer): The PaintLayer class in third_party/blink/renderer/core/paint/paint_layer.h (line 174) represents stacking contexts and establishes the paint tree structure. PaintLayers handle compositing, clipping, and z-ordering of visual elements.\\n\\n4. **Display Items and Paint Recording**: Two key classes handle paint recording:\\n   - DisplayItemList (third_party/blink/renderer/platform/graphics/paint/display_item_list.h, line 28) stores the list of paint operations\\n   - PaintController (third_party/blink/renderer/platform/graphics/paint/paint_controller.h, line 131) manages the recording of display items during the paint phase\\n\\nThe pipeline flow: CSS changes \u2192 StyleResolver resolves styles \u2192 LayoutObject computes layout based on styles \u2192 PaintLayer organizes the paint tree \u2192 PaintController records display items for rendering.\"\n}\n",
